➜不必远赴日本，40个魔都日式体验带你梦回霓虹！
http://www.sohu.com/a/429144288_380622	11921
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201103/46d51143de95420ba05c36bb51560d87.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
